    "description": "<strong>Zombie Warz</strong> = RTS + Roguelite + survivor<br><br><strong>Zombie Warz</strong> is a mash up of <strong>base building, survival, rts, tower defense and zombie horde mode</strong> with <strong>unlockable </strong>progression and <strong>roguelite </strong>gameplay for <strong>replayability</strong>. <br><br>Play as the <strong>king </strong>of a kingdom under siege by <strong>zombies </strong>and discover their origins.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build up your kingdom</strong> </h2>Gather resources and units to grow.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Modify the battlefield</strong></h2>Build defenses and use a variety of items to fight the zombies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299490/extras/2a6ddff8e4018aac377e70bc3e62eb65.poster.avif?t=1716978740\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299490/extras/2a6ddff8e4018aac377e70bc3e62eb65.webm?t=1716978740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299490/extras/2a6ddff8e4018aac377e70bc3e62eb65.mp4?t=1716978740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ALL OUT WAR!</strong></h2>Will the kingdom you have built survive the zombie hordes?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299490/extras/a19d0ae4a889cc9a7a534fd2af000865.poster.avif?t=1716978740\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299490/extras/a19d0ae4a889cc9a7a534fd2af000865.webm?t=1716978740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2299490/extras/a19d0ae4a889cc9a7a534fd2af000865.mp4?t=1